SQL_STMT_U.val: Select distinct DEBC.DEBC_ADMNO, DEBC.DEBC_CLNTNO, DEBH.DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY from :1/DEBC DEBC join :1/DEBH DEBH on DEBC.DEBC_DEBH = DEBH.DEBH_NO join :1/ADMN ADMN on DEBC.DEBC_ADMNO = ADMN.ADMN_NO exception join :1/CCRY CCRY on CCRY.CCRY308_ADMNO = DEBC.DEBC_ADMNO and CCRY.CCRY308_CLNTNO = DEBC.DEBC_CLNTNO and CCRY.CCRY308_COUNTRY = DEBH.DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY where DEBC.DEBC_DATDELETED is null and ADMN.ADMN_DELCREDERE = 'N' ORDER BY DEBC.DEBC_ADMNO, DEBC.DEBC_CLNTNO, DEBH.DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY for fetch only

Select count(*) from :1/DEBC DEBC join :1/DEBH DEBH on DEBC.DEBC_DEBH = DEBH.DEBH_NO join :1/ADMN ADMN on DEBC.DEBC_ADMNO = ADMN.ADMN_NO exception join :1/CCRY CCRY on CCRY.CCRY308_ADMNO = DEBC.DEBC_ADMNO and CCRY.CCRY308_CLNTNO = DEBC.DEBC_CLNTNO and CCRY.CCRY308_COUNTRY = DEBH.DEBH_HADR_COUNTRY where DEBC.DEBC_DATDELETED is null and ADMN.ADMN_DELCREDERE = 'N'

select CLNT101_ADMNO, CLNT102_CLNTNO from :1/CLNT, :1/ADMN where CLNT906_STATUSCONTRACT = 1 and CLNT212_FCI = 0 and ADMN_NO = CLNT101_ADMNO and ADMN_DELCREDERE = 'N' and ADMN_TESTCLIENTS = 'N' and ADMN_ENDCLIENTS = 'N' and exists (select * from :1/DOCP where DOCP_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and DOCP_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO)
